      "\t[1] Influence of small amounts of Si and Cr on the high-temperature oxidation behavior of novel cobalt base superalloys, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1016/j.corsci.2021.109388\n",
      "\t[2] High Temperature Oxidation Behavior of a Novel γ′-Strengthened CoNi-Base Superalloy, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1007/s11085-023-10214-x\n",
